<Layout>
    <main class="">
		<div class="flex -z-10 bg-cover object-center min-w-full bg-center bg-no-repeat w-full pt-24" style="background-image:url('/iedcdesign/img/AdobeStock_582485671.jpeg')">
		<div class="text-center py-7 container">
			<h1 class="md:text-8xl uppercase font-extrabold text-blue-900 text-5xl">
                 iedc Best Practices
			</h1>

		</div>
		</div>

		
	</main>

  <section class="pt-24 px-12 ">
			<div class=" md:flex-row mx-auto flex col md:space-x-4 space-x-0 ">
				<div class="flex md:w-1/3 w-full mx-auto md:mt-10">
					<img src="/iedcdesign/img/iedc_web/ig.png" class=" rounded-3xl object-center h-96 mx-auto">
				</div>
				<div class=" md:w-2/3 w-full  my-auto">
					<h1 class="md:text-4xl text-3xl text-blue-900 font-extrabold text-center pb-10">Best Practices of IEDCs</h1>
					
					<p class="text-justify text-xl">KSUM has decided to capture the evolution, Best practices, Innovation, and case studies of IEDCs and has designed a Knowledge Management Framework.</p>
					<p class="text-xl py-5">The objective of this Knowledge Management Exercise are as follows:-</p>
    <ul class="text-xl px-5 " >
    <li>-To facilitate the capturing of the evolving changes in IEDC policies, structures, strategies, processes, and interventions and justifications established and outcomes/impacts achieved</li>
    <li>-To document and create a knowledge repository containing best practices, innovations, and case studies at various levels of IEDC.</li>
    <li>-To enable utilization of the knowledge accumulated for application into future practices and decision-making.</li>
    </ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>


    <section  class="py-24 px-12 text-justify">
    <div>
 
    
    <p class="text-xl  py-10">You are requested to share your Institution Best Practices. And the shortlisted Best Practices and Case studies will be presented in the Knowledge Management Workshop scheduled to be held in the first week of October 2021. Subsequently, selected best practices and case studies will be compiled and published.</p>
    <h1 class=" text-2xl  text-blue-900 font-bold py-5">How to Apply?</h1>
    <ul class="text-xl px-10 py-5">
    <li>-The application is now open and you can refer the attached documents and upload the details in the format attached by 30th September 2021 in the INNOVATE Portal under the Module - “PROJECTS” (in the IEDC Knowledge Management Framework).</li>
    <li>-Click on the “APPLY TO THE PROJECT” button in the PROJECT Module.</li>
    <li>-Please upload the best practices you have collated from your institution in the prescribed format.</li>
    </ul>
    </div>

    <div class=" flex md:flex-row flex-col pt-10 text-xl text-white px-15 mx-10 md:space-x-5 space-x-0 ">
          <div class=" hover:bg-gray-800  flex flex-row py-9 px-5 border-l-2 border-gray-500  bg-orange-500 hover:animate-bounce"><h1 class=" text-white font bold">Application Open Date</h1><p class"text-white"> :<span class="bg-blue-900 text-white font-bold px-2 py-3 justify-center rounded-full text-center mx-2"> 9th</span> Sept 2021</p></div>
          <div class=" hover:bg-gray-800 flex flex-row  py-9 px-5 border-l-2 border-gray-500  bg-orange-500 hover:animate-bounce"><h1 class="  text-white font bold">Application End Date</h1><p class"text-white">: <span class="bg-blue-900 text-white font-bold px-2 py-3 justify-center rounded-full text-center mx-2"> 30th </span> Sept 2021</p></div>
          <div class=" hover:bg-gray-800 flex flex-row py-9 px-5 border-l-2 border-gray-500  bg-orange-500 hover:animate-bounce"><h1 class="  text-white font bold">Workshop Date </h1><p class"text-white">: <span class="bg-blue-900 text-white font-bold px-2 py-3 justify-center rounded-full text-center mx-2">First week </span> of Oct 2021</p></div>
    </div>
    </section>




    
